        "source_site": "toolbox",
        "listing_url": "https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/2023/09/what-is-relationship-marketing-and-how-will-it-help-you/",
        "slug": "what-is-relationship-marketing-and-how-will-it-help-you",
        "title": "What is Relationship Marketing and how will it help you?",
        "excerpt": "",
        "published_at": "",
        "category": "",
        "featured_image_url": "",
        "content_html": "<div class=\\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\\"><div class=\\"article-meta\\">\\r\\n            <div class=\\"article-meta-inner\\">\\r\\n                <span class=\\"byline\\" itemprop=\\"author\\">\\r\\n                    <span class=\\"author\\">\\r\\n                        <a href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/author/ebernick/\\" class=\\"url fn\\">\\r\\n                            <img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c93c8b79f7e98017d711a76defef518dcbeed7b9509a4035ef1852034150bd61?s=120&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\\" srcset=\\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c93c8b79f7e98017d711a76defef518dcbeed7b9509a4035ef1852034150bd61?s=240&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\\" class=\\"avatar avatar-120 photo\\" height=\\"120\\" width=\\"120\\" decoding=\\"async\\">ebernick                        </a>\\r\\n                    </span>\\r\\n                </span>\\r\\n            </div>\\r\\n        </div>       \\r\\n    <div class=\\"content-wrap\\">    <div class=\\"entry-content\\" itemprop=\\"text\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\n<p>Relationship marketing is a sales strategy which focuses on how to build relationships with prospects, thus converting them into customers. This ongoing relationship, which differentiates you from your competitors, ensures that they will buy from you over and over again. Learn what steps to follow in building meaningful relationships with your customers\\u2026</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>At the center of Relationship Marketing are\\u00a0four very important elements:</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<ul class=\\"wp-block-list\\">\\n<li><strong>You need to be trustworthy</strong></li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li><strong>You need to be unique</strong></li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li><strong>You have to be able to deliver what is expected from you</strong></li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li><strong>You need to have the ability to \\u201cconnect\\u201d with people</strong></li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>In the new paperback publication \\u201cSuccessful Selling Unlocked \\u2013 Relationship Marketing\\u201d</strong>\\u00a0you will be taken by the hand and led through the process from start to finish.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>Part One</strong>\\u00a0summarises the basic steps of the selling process. Some of you might already know this, but going back to basics and building from there is always a good idea. Just look at sports\\u2026 the teams who do the basics right are the ones who end up winners, and the same is true\\u00a0in selling.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>For those of you who\\u00a0are new to selling,\\u00a0this section will provide you with the foundation\\u00a0on which\\u00a0you can start building.</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>In\\u00a0<strong>Part Two</strong>\\u00a0we delve deeper and find out\\u00a0<strong>what has changed in the sales process and why these changes have taken place</strong>. This knowledge will allow you to\\u00a0<strong>better understand your clients</strong>\\u00a0and teach you how to adapt and\\u00a0respond to these changes effectively.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>We look more closely at the customer of today. There is nothing more valuable than\\u00a0<strong>knowing exactly what it is your customer expects</strong>. With this knowledge you will know how to\\u00a0<strong>get the trust of your customers and keep it.</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>You are taken by the hand and taught how to\\u00a0<strong>develop a winning strategy</strong>\\u00a0in the form of a practical Relationship Marketing plan\\u00a0for your business or product/service. Then learn how to put this plan into action all the way through to a successful result.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>In\\u00a0<strong>Part Three</strong>\\u00a0you will\\u00a0<strong>discover the \\u2018soft skills\\u2019</strong>\\u00a0that are designed to help you\\u00a0<strong>develop the art of \\u2018connecting\\u2019 with other people</strong>. You will learn the importance of personal development and how to keep a positive attitude no matter what.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Your personal development and attitude are\\u00a0<strong>the two factors that will set you apart and</strong> help you reach the heights you never thought possible.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Throughout the book,\\u00a0<strong>real life examples and experiences are used</strong>\\u00a0to help you to make practical applications of the principles and strategy discussed. The use of many illustrations (examples, stories, exemplifications) contributes to an appealing and enjoyable learning process.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>The book clears up the misconception that successful selling is limited to an elite few.\\u00a0<strong>It is within the reach of anyone</strong>\\u00a0who has the ability to be a friend, which includes virtually everyone. Furthermore, it reveals that selling is fun and exciting!</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>\\u201cContact Eberhard <a rel=\\"noreferrer noopener\\" href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">TODAY</a> for your <u><a rel=\\"noreferrer noopener\\" href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">FREE 30-minute Zoom CONSULTATION</a></u> to learn more about how to unlock your potential and accelerate the results you want in your life.\\u201d</strong></p>\\n\\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\\r\\n    \\t<footer class=\\"entry-footer\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\\r\\n\\t</div></div>",
