        "title": "Enthusiasm Unlocks Your Potential",
        "excerpt": "",
        "published_at": "",
        "category": "",
        "featured_image_url": "",
        "content_html": "<div class=\\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\\"><div class=\\"article-meta\\">\\r\\n            <div class=\\"article-meta-inner\\">\\r\\n                <span class=\\"byline\\" itemprop=\\"author\\">\\r\\n                    <span class=\\"author\\">\\r\\n                        <a href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/author/ebernick/\\" class=\\"url fn\\">\\r\\n                            <img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c93c8b79f7e98017d711a76defef518dcbeed7b9509a4035ef1852034150bd61?s=120&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\\" srcset=\\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c93c8b79f7e98017d711a76defef518dcbeed7b9509a4035ef1852034150bd61?s=240&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\\" class=\\"avatar avatar-120 photo\\" height=\\"120\\" width=\\"120\\" decoding=\\"async\\">ebernick                        </a>\\r\\n                    </span>\\r\\n                </span>\\r\\n            </div>\\r\\n        </div>       \\r\\n    <div class=\\"content-wrap\\">    <div class=\\"entry-content\\" itemprop=\\"text\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\n<p>In my series of blog articles outlining the catalyst for realizing your inner potential, I have been using each letter in the word INVEST (being used as an acronym) to highlight an aspect of \\u201cInvesting in you potential\\u201d . We have already discussed the first three letters, namely \\u201cI\\u201d for Inspiration, \\u201cN\\u201d for No Problems, Only Opportunities, and \\u201cV\\u201d for Vision.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>In our discussion of the next letter in the acronym \\u201cINVEST\\u201d (IN YOUR POTENTIAL), the letter \\u201cE\\u201d stands for ENTHUSIASM.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>One dictionary describes enthusiasm as a \\u201cstrong excitement for something you like or enjoy\\u201d</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Enthusiasm is a game changer! People with enthusiasm go through life with an air of confidence that they can achieve whatever they put their mind to. Minor day-to-day difficulties are swept aside as if they did not exist. Their words have power, their eyes sparkle. Others who come into contact with them are attracted to them. Enthusiasm is powerful in its ability to enthuse both yourself and others who come into contact with you.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>If enthusiasm is so powerful, the question arises, \\u201cWhy don\\u2019t more people have enthusiasm?\\u201d</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>I guess the answer is that some people are \\u201cwaiting for enthusiasm to come to them\\u201d. These people will wait a long time, because enthusiasm does not \\u201ccome to you\\u201d. You have to \\u201cgo to it\\u201d. You have to generate your own enthusiasm! I am going to give you a simple tool to achieve this. The power of this tool is in the doing of it.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Write down 3 lists as follows:</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<ol class=\\"wp-block-list\\">\\n<li>10 Reasons why it is good to be alive</li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li>10 Reasons why it is advantageous for others to have my product or services</li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li>10 reasons why it is important for me to be a success</li>\\n</ol>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Then, take a few moments to read these lists daily. As you focus on the meaning of these personal reasons, you will \\u201cgo to enthusiasm\\u201d. You will generate enthusiasm for yourself, and it will put a spring in your step, a smile on your face, and a positive energy into your soul.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Add \\u201cEnthusiasm\\u201d to the first three ingredients already outlined, namely, \\u201cInspiration\\u201d, \\u201cNo Problems, Only Opportunities\\u201d and \\u201cVision\\u201d to realise your personal power within you.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><em>\\u201cEverything you have is within you. All you need is a catalyst to bring it out\\u201d</em>\\u2013 Author Unknown</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>In my next blog we will reveal what the \\u201cS\\u201d in INVEST stands for.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>(Eberhard Niklaus empowers people and teams by helping them unlock their strengths, thereby helping your team to maximize performance, productivity and profitability)</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>\\u201cContact Eberhard <a rel=\\"noreferrer noopener\\" href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">TODAY</a> for your <a rel=\\"noreferrer noopener\\" href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">FREE 30-minute Zoom CONSULTATION</a> to learn more about how to unlock your potential and accelerate the results you want in your life.\\u201d</strong></p>\\n\\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\\r\\n    \\t<footer class=\\"entry-footer\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\\r\\n\\t</div></div>",
