        "source_site": "toolbox",
        "listing_url": "https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/2023/09/why-you-cannot-afford-not-to-coach-your-staff-grow-performance-by-more-than-20/",
        "slug": "why-you-cannot-afford-not-to-coach-your-staff-grow-performance-by-more-than-20",
        "title": "Why You Cannot Afford Not to Coach Your Staff (Grow Performance by more than 20%)",
        "excerpt": "",
        "published_at": "",
        "category": "",
        "featured_image_url": "",
        "content_html": "<div class=\\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\\"><div class=\\"article-meta\\">\\r\\n            <div class=\\"article-meta-inner\\">\\r\\n                <span class=\\"byline\\" itemprop=\\"author\\">\\r\\n                    <span class=\\"author\\">\\r\\n                        <a href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/author/ebernick/\\" class=\\"url fn\\">\\r\\n                            <img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c93c8b79f7e98017d711a76defef518dcbeed7b9509a4035ef1852034150bd61?s=120&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\\" srcset=\\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c93c8b79f7e98017d711a76defef518dcbeed7b9509a4035ef1852034150bd61?s=240&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\\" class=\\"avatar avatar-120 photo\\" height=\\"120\\" width=\\"120\\" decoding=\\"async\\">ebernick                        </a>\\r\\n                    </span>\\r\\n                </span>\\r\\n            </div>\\r\\n        </div>       \\r\\n    <div class=\\"content-wrap\\">    <div class=\\"entry-content\\" itemprop=\\"text\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\n<p>Can you \\u201cfix a weakness?\\u201d Have you sent any of your staff for training to \\u201cfix their weaknesses?\\u201d Are you focused on helping your kids with their perceived weaknesses?</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>If you answered \\u201cYes\\u201d to any of the above questions, you may be surprised to hear me telling you that \\u201cyou cannot fix a weakness\\u201d. Successful people who perform the best are people who do the following:</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<ol class=\\"wp-block-list\\">\\n<li>Identify their strengths.</li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li>Understand their strengths.</li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li>Apply (fit) their strengths in their work to produce great results and add to the bottom line.</li>\\n\\n\\n\\n<li>Manage their weaknesses with their strengths.</li>\\n</ol>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>Fact:\\u00a0</strong>People who spend their time doing what they do best display the greatest productivity and profitability.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Just doing more of what you do best can dramatically improve your performance. That\\u2019s the simple part. The more complex part is finding out how to do that in your present role, or finding another role that allows you to do that.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>If you are a sales manager or a small business owner, would you agree that coaching your staff (and yourself) to do the above would produce enhanced performance and profitability? Can you afford not to benefit from coaching?</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>As a business coach, I can help you identify the Top 5 Strengths of each of your staff. I can also coach them to understand how these talent themes can be applied to their work to grow their performance by at least 20%.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Can you afford not to have coaching as part of your \\u201cInvestment Policy\\u201d? Your staff are the biggest asset in your business. When Hal Rosenbluth, CEO of Rosenbluth International, was asked what the most important factor was for his business success, he replied \\u201cThe Customer comes second\\u201d. \\u201cWho comes first?\\u2019 he was asked. \\u201cMy employees\\u201d he answered. What he was saying is that if you genuinely want to put the customer first, you must put your employees more first!</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p>Do you want your business to grow? Invest in your people and \\u201cwatch this space!\\u201d</p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p><strong>\\u201cContact Eberhard <a rel=\\"noreferrer noopener\\" href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">TODAY</a> for your <u><a rel=\\"noreferrer noopener\\" href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">FREE 30-minute Zoom CONSULTATION</a></u> to learn more about how to unlock your potential and accelerate the results you want in your life.\\u201d</strong></p>\\n\\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\\r\\n    \\t<footer class=\\"entry-footer\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\\r\\n\\t</div></div>",
