 href=\\"https://www.thestrengthstoolbox.com/calendar/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">FREE 30-minute Zoom CONSULTATION</a></u> to learn more about how to unlock your potential and accelerate the results you want in your life.\\u201d</strong></p>\\n\\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\\r\\n    \\t<footer class=\\"entry-footer\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\\r\\n\\t</div></div>",
